svg.title: Zombie Massacre

g.text: 1. Use the WASD keys to move around.
2. Avoid incoming zombies. Do NOT touch them.
3. You should also shoot and kill them zombies by clicking on them.
4. Some zombies may take more than one hit to kill them.
5. In the end there is a BOSS. Keep shooting it to kill it. A health bar will show its health.
